h27 ydaf ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of God, as revealed in the sacrifice of His only-begotten Son, and many were </div><div class="t m12e x26 h27 ya43 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">led to inquire, What must I do to be saved?&quot;—The </div><div class="t m663 x44 h16 y53c ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Acts of the Apostles, </div><div class="t m638 x179 h27 y53c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. </div><div class="t m1669 x26 h27 y595 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">208. </div><div class="t m2f9 x64 h27 y603 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">If it had been possible the Galatians would have given their eyes to </div><div class="t m34a x18 h27 y76a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Paul. &quot;Paul had a bodily affliction; his &apos;eyesight was bad.&quot;—Ellen G. </div><div class="t mec4 x18 h27 y77c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">White comments, </div><div class="t m1310 x39 h16 y77c ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SDA Bible Commentary, </div><div class="t m374 x9 h27 y8b3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vol. 6, p. 1107. </div><div class="t m1db x64 h27 y2a1 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What a contrast was their present attitude to Paul! Sadly the apostle </div><div class="t m1080 x18 h27 y3f2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">asks, &quot;Have I now become your enemy by telling you the truth?&quot; (Gal. </div><div class="t m412 x18 h27 y1322 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4:16, NIV). </div><div class="t m68e x29 h87 y405 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Making Paul&apos;s experience your own. • </div><div class="t m34e x64 h27 y3a5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m1648 x6f h27 y3a5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Can you identify a time in your life when God used a great trial to </div><div class="t m172f x29 h27 yf8a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lead you where He wanted you to go? </div><div class="t m34e x64 h27 y2a4 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m7fa x66 h27 y13ea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What blessings have you received through ministry to someone in </div><div class="t m46a x29 h27 y5d5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">need? Do you know